######################################################################################
# Modifications :
#     FRRIC - 07/02/12 - EXI 44459
#              - Rajout du tableau pour Handicap (Flag,Taux de handicap et Date d‚but et de fin)
#     MABOS - 09/01/2013-US1130-FQ81085- The user can type an authorization depending on another legislation
#             - field HAB: Replace Data type ADI by Alpha -Add actions to make it works as an ADI with a different control
#     MABOS - 11/04/13 - FQ71754 - US1516- Remove the control on the civility 2 (Mrs./Madame)
#                                          to give the possibility to add the birth Name in all cases.
#     SEGAY - 12/12/13 - FQ94474 US2231 : Rate of handicap not mandatory
#     SEGAY - 14/03/14 - FQ96993 US2520 : No test overlapping with one of the periods already entered
